<h3>Old And New Songs on the Dull Topic of Fiscal Responsibility and Social Justice</h3>

I recently jotted down a terribly rough start to a song aboun current
events in July, 2011. It's called <a href="./whichside.html">Which
Side Are You On?</a>. Normally I try to see both sides of arguments,
sometimes succeed, this time I end up feeling strongly that one side
is plain duplcities and insidious and it's time to say so. Well, see
what you think.

<p>

An old song on a that same long-term theme goes by the scintillating
title of "Fiscal Policy." There have been a few requests for the
words, so <a href="./fiscal.html">here they are</a>.

<br>

